==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Devotee
<hw>Dev`o*tee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is wholly
devoted; esp., one given wholly to religion; one who is superstitiously
given to religious duties and ceremonies; a bigot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>While Father Le Blanc was very devout he was not a
<qex>devotee</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>A. S. Hardy.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Devotement</ent>⟦br⟧
